{"tid":2511273,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我真係一個仆街","createTime":"2021-04-30T19:09:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T19:46:29.000Z","uid":333274,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f6e5c5074c6145fd469de2f93c5b06d3880ae2b4","tid":2511273,"uid":333274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T19:09:03.000Z","msg":"我曾經係一個MK妹<br />\n15歲搬出去同男朋友住<br />\n仲比人搞大肚<br />\n去過黑市落又去過家計會落<br />\n到分手嘅一刻先知道自己原來幾冇用<br />\n每日都唔知係到做梗咩<br />\n到直我認識到一個男朋友<br />\n佢同我之前個男朋友好唔同<br />\n佢唔比我飲酒 唔比我食煙<br />\n對我好似公主咁好<br />\n仲鼓勵我去讀書 鼓勵我去追夢<br />\n當全世界嘅人都認為我唔得 連我自己都咁認為<br />\n但佢信我 真係唔知點解<br />\n我嘅夢想係成為一位護士<br />\n去幫有需要嘅人 去幫無能為力嘅人<br />\n最終我用左幾年時間去讀書<br />\n最後我地都係分左手 我真係好感激佢<br />\n但我地性格真係唔適合<br />\n老士啲講 如果明知我唔愛佢<br />\n但一直同佢一齊 真係利用梗佢<br />\n分手後 我知道佢因為我心情好差<br />\n好似放棄左自己咁 成日去飲酒食大麻<br />\n我唔知點幫佢<br />\n我試過同佢傾 但佢態度一樣 <br />\n好想知佢近況 但又唔敢再搵佢<br />\n怕佢再傷心 真係唔知點做"},{"pid":"720e8fa89a1d1f8ebe826ab30758b6bc35a2b805","tid":2511273,"uid":7102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T19:12:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03e6ac94a8688e71c14f68688206c9f146bdf916","tid":2511273,"uid":187153,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T19:23:08.000Z","msg":"就係一個仆街"},{"pid":"89afe08314f086fbebc8d0deb76301d401d231ed","tid":2511273,"uid":214456,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T19:28:33.000Z","msg":"你努力過得好就夠 佢會知道的"},{"pid":"adc2dcdb3d17a015782f2a9f92dd70c497a795ba","tid":2511273,"uid":186431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T19:28:56.000Z","msg":"我近況係性慾好強<br />\n呢排成日去叫雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"205a4b494d25cbe0eb6adbb1e31df879f67a7f4e","tid":2511273,"uid":3253,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T19:29:41.000Z","msg":"你唔係仆街 只係正宗肉便器 係男人都上得果隻"},{"pid":"7da1198e2f378ae232bc0a9ad9f66432f5fd7ba3","tid":2511273,"uid":366655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T19:37:40.000Z","msg":"How much<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/cigar.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf08d3607e3c8dbfd21b36ef803df43bb4da2a52","tid":2511273,"uid":374353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T19:40:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5Li7wpz2Mw4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D5Li7wpz2Mw4&d=TdbSzDXFtRyzmt3f81zqRJggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=bd2a1d77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5Li7wpz2Mw4</a><br />\n希望絲打睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74b3fa3a5d23b4a0f1544e735b2691dce2ab99b7","tid":2511273,"uid":374353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T19:42:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/ZJJC7ia51y8/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FZJJC7ia51y8%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=27500877&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2765b41b2f002aeac002a3424afbffea9d3da1d6","tid":2511273,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T19:44:28.000Z","msg":"借黎屌兩野ok?"},{"pid":"57a47ffb8b5b437db4871b737e84a5e309f101a8","tid":2511273,"uid":359419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T19:46:29.000Z","msg":"我以前很垃圾，沒有價值可言，<br />\n直到他改變了我，陪著我，<br />\n我也漸漸改變自己命運了，<br />\n他可以說是令我成為護士的踏腳石，<br />\n我認識了一個醫生，<br />\n我選擇和他分手了，<br />\n他開始變了，變得墮落，<br />\n幸好沒跟他繼續一起。"}]}